xample, the maximal contribution of the block-relating\neffects amounts to a few percent of the prescribed dose.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Nov 2008 13:23:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Nov 2008 14:56:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Nov 2008 12:19:08 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 5 Dec 2008 08:16:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-12-05"}
