oidal field of order of 10**14 Gauss, sufficient to explain long\ngamma-ray bursts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Nov 2008 09:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Jan 2009 09:55:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
